        <div class="bodysection">
            <div class="body" itemprop="about" data-fieldname="body" data-bind="htmlValue:body"><p>dystopolis returns to the big screen this winter due to popular demand.</p>
<p>featuring the original film (including credits), plus the film of the film and a q&amp;a session with the writer/producer/director about this ongoing project and the opportunities to get involved in future film production.</p>
<p>itinerant motion picture company are starting production on the follow-up to this well recieved mini-epic. "noctambule;triptych act II" is currently casting but the search is really on for aspiring producers.</p>

<p>www.imdb.com/title/tt1950147/</p></div>
